  "None suggested yet": "Belum ada saran",
  "After the AI responds, a separate quiet API call generates the tracker JSON independently. Expect ~250–300s total per message (narrative + wait + tracker).": "Setelah AI merespons, panggilan diam menghasilkan JSON. ~250–300 detik.",
  "✓ Single API call — typically ~100–120s total": "✓ Satu panggilan API — ~100–120 detik",
  "✓ No profile switching — eliminates message deletion risk": "✓ Tanpa ganti profil — tanpa risiko",
  "✓ AI has full narrative context for accurate tracking": "✓ AI memiliki konteks lengkap",
  "✓ 2–3× faster than Separate mode in practice": "✓ 2–3× lebih cepat dari Terpisah",
  "✗ Uses tokens from the main response budget (~1,700 tokens for tracker)": "✗ Menggunakan token dari anggaran utama (~1.700)",
  "✗ May slightly reduce narrative length on token-limited models": "✗ Dapat sedikit mengurangi panjang narasi",
  "✓ Clean responses — narrative never token-competes with tracker": "✓ Respons bersih — tanpa persaingan",
  "✓ Dedicated token budget for tracker output": "✓ Anggaran khusus untuk pelacak",
  "✓ Can use a different connection profile/preset": "✓ Dapat menggunakan profil/preset berbeda",
  "✗ Two API calls per message — 2–3× slower than Together mode": "✗ Dua panggilan API — 2–3× lebih lambat",
  "✗ ~12s dead time between calls (chat save + preset switching)": "✗ ~12 detik jeda antara panggilan",
  "✗ Tracker prompt is ~10K+ tokens at 8 context msgs — reduce to 3–4 for speed": "✗ Prompt ~10K+ di 8 pesan — kurangi ke 3–4",
  "✗ Profile switching can cause message deletion (race condition with other extensions)": "✗ Pergantian profil dapat menghapus pesan",
  "✗ Embeds previous snapshot into narrative call (~1.9K tokens) unless Embed snapshots = 0": "✗ Menyematkan snapshot sebelumnya (~1.9K) kecuali = 0",
  "How many recent messages to include when generating tracker updates.": "Berapa pesan terbaru untuk disertakan.",
  "Separate mode only — Together mode uses ST's full context automatically.": "Hanya Terpisah — Bersama menggunakan konteks ST.",
  "Fastest. Good for simple 1-on-1 scenes (~5K token prompt)": "Tercepat. Untuk adegan 1-lawan-1 (~5K)",
  "Balanced. Recommended for most scenes (~8–12K tokens)": "Seimbang. Untuk kebanyakan (~8–12K)",
  "Better continuity for complex multi-character scenes (~12–20K tokens)": "Kontinuitas lebih baik untuk adegan kompleks (~12–20K)",
  "Maximum context but significantly slower and more expensive": "Konteks maksimum tetapi lebih lambat dan mahal",
  "This is the biggest factor in Separate mode speed. At 8 msgs your tracker prompt is ~10K tokens — doubling roughly doubles generation time. Lower values (3–4) can cut tracker time by 40–60%.": "Faktor terbesar. 8 pesan ~10K — menggandakan waktu. 3–4 mengurangi 40–60%.",
  "Separate mode only.": "Hanya mode Terpisah.",
  "How many times to retry if the tracker API call returns invalid JSON.": "Berapa kali mencoba ulang jika JSON tidak valid.",
  "Built-in preset: temp=0.6, top_p=0.95, freq_pen=0.15, max_tokens=4096. Optimized for structured JSON output on GLM-5.": "Preset: temp=0.6, top_p=0.95, freq_pen=0.15, max_tokens=4096. Untuk JSON di GLM-5.",
  "Embed recent scene snapshots into the narrative conversation context so the AI can reference tracker state while writing. Only applies in Separate mode. The tracker's own API call always receives the previous snapshot regardless of this setting.": "Menyematkan snapshot ke konteks. Hanya Terpisah. Pelacak selalu menerima sebelumnya.",
  "Each embedded snapshot adds ~1.9K tokens to your narrative prompt. Set to 0 to eliminate this overhead — the tracker API call still receives previous state independently. Set to 1 for narrative continuity (AI remembers scene details). Values above 1 are rarely beneficial.": "Setiap snapshot +~1.9K. 0 untuk menghilangkan. 1 untuk kontinuitas. Di atas 1 jarang berguna.",
  "Injected as invisible context — AI treats it as authoritative background info. Best for continuity without polluting the conversation.": "Diinjeksikan sebagai konteks tak terlihat — info resmi.",
  "Appears as if the user said it — some models respond more attentively.": "Tampil seolah pengguna berkata — beberapa model lebih perhatian.",
